The paper discusses the application of machine learning, specifically Convolutional Neural Network (CNN), to Question Answering Systems (QAS). This falls under the sub-category of Natural Language Processing (NLP) which is covered by cs.CL. The paper also mentions the use of large datasets and word embeddings, which are common techniques in Information Retrieval (IR) and Machine Learning (ML) respectively, leading to the possibility of the paper being categorized under cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.NE as well.
